latestPosts.caption:
What happens when you swap dating apps for dares, icebreakers, and actual eye contact?

I went to a speed dating event by @small.world thinking it’d be chill…
Instead, I got hit with pickup lines, random dares, and people actually shooting their shot.

Was it chaotic? Yes.
Was it hilarious? Also yes.
Did someone ask if I believe in love at first sip (of chai)? Unfortunately… yes again.

If dating apps are dry, maybe it’s time to go analog.
Would you try something like this?
